<h3 class="CTSTitle orange">Take Action</h3>
<p class="CTSParagraph">Participating in a clinical trial is an invaluable way to get involved in the pursuit of a cure for Parkinson’s disease. <strong>No amount of funding or other resources can make up for a lack of volunteers.</strong></p>
